<div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #111; max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto;">
  <h2 style="color: #111;">Invoice {{invoiceNumber}}</h2>
  <p>Hi {{buyerName}},</p>
  <p>Your invoice <strong>{{invoiceNumber}}</strong> from {{sellerName}} is ready.</p>

  <table cellpadding="8" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse: collapse; margin: 16px 0; width: 100%;">
    <tr>
      <td style="border: 1px solid #ddd;">Issued On</td>
      <td style="border: 1px solid #ddd;">{{createdAt}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="border: 1px solid #ddd;">Due Date</td>
      <td style="border: 1px solid #ddd;">{{dueDate}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="border: 1px solid #ddd;">Total</td>
      <td style="border: 1px solid #ddd;"><strong>{{currency}} {{totalAmount}}</strong></td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <p>You can download the invoice anytime using the link below:</p>
  <p>
    <a href="{{downloadUrl}}" style="background:#111;color:#fff;padding:10px 16px;text-decoration:none;border-radius:4px;">
      View Invoice
    </a>
  </p>

  <p>The invoice PDF and e-way bill (where applicable) are attached for your reference.</p>
  <p style="color:#555;">Thank you,<br/>SwiftShip AI Billing</p>
</div>
